title: Q&A: Alyona Mysko of Ukraine-based Fuel Finance - Practical Ecommerce
content: Q&A: Alyona Mysko of Ukraine-based Fuel Finance  Practical Ecommerce
description: Fuel Finance is a Ukraine-based "financial department in the cloud." Alyona Myskyo launched the company two and a half years ago to provide easy-to-follow info to help merchants with quick decision-making.
